phemes.FromString(text)\ng.AnsiEscapeSequences = true\n\nfor g.Next() {\n\tfmt.Println(g.Value())\n}\n```\n\nTo also parse 8-bit C1 controls (non-UTF-8 bytes), set `AnsiEscapeSequences8Bit` to true.\n\n```go\ng.AnsiEscapeSequences = true     // 7-bit forms (ESC ...)\ng.AnsiEscapeSequences8Bit = true // 8-bit C1 forms (0x80-0x9F), not valid UTF-8\n```\n\nFor ESC-initiated (7-bit) control strings, only 7-bit terminators are recognized.\nFor C1-initiated (8-bit) control strings, only C1 ST (`0x9C`) is recognized as ST.\n\nWe implement [ECMA-48","target":"https://ecma-international.org/publications-and-standards/standards/ecma-48/","line":80},{"title":"`utf8.Valid()`","target":"https://pkg.go.dev/unicode/utf8#Valid","line":120}],"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[[9,11],[13,22],[37,44],[50,61],[65,73],[79,87],[91,94],[103,114]]},"smart_blocks:sources/podman/vendor/github.com/clipperhouse/uax29/v2/graphemes/README.md#": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":null},"embeddings":{},"text":null,"length":0,"last_read":{"hash":"1v5hna3","at":1782387048689},"key":"sources/podman/vendor/github.com/clipperhouse/uax29/v2/graphemes/README.md#","lines":[1,6],"size":500,"outlinks":[{"title":"Unicode text segmentation","target":"https://unicode.org/reports/tr29/#Grapheme_Cluster_Boundaries","line":1},{"title":"![Documentation","target":"https://pkg.go.dev/badge/github.com/clipperhouse/uax29/v2/graphemes.svg","line":3},{"title":"Tests","target":"https://github.com/clipperhouse/uax29/actions/workflows/gotest.yml/badge.svg","line":4,"embedded":true},{"title":"Fuzz","target":"https://github.com/clipperhouse/uax29/actions/workflows/gofuzz.yml/badge.svg","line":5,"embedded":true}],"class_name":"SmartBlock"},
